<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5179515>
    dc:description "Figures 1-2. 1) Lissohypnus texanus, habitus of female, 8 mm long. 1a) head further magnified showing ocular punctures (arrowed). 2) Lissohypnus fullertoni, habitus of male holotype, 7.5 mm long, 2a) head further magnified showing ocular punctures (arrowed), 2b) tergite VIII, 2c) genital segment, dorsal side up, 2d) aedeagus (with fovea arrowed)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5179515/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

